{"tid":2121785,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"當香港不再香港時","createTime":"2020-07-23T14:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T14:28:44.000Z","uid":309331,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f0efe70915371d697bffa2da53469172011870a","tid":2121785,"uid":309331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:07:25.000Z","msg":"我啊爸有段好香港嘅經歴 想分享吓<br />\n希望冇香港身份認同嘅年輕人聽到會有感觸 雖然佢記得唔多 但係佢嘅乖仔識gg 仲揾返以前嘅相畀佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啊爸48年喺香港出世 出身時屋企一貧如洗 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">~1937-1945 /1948</span><br />\n佢啊爸(爺) 本身住喺廣東省增城區(東莞上面) 戰後3年啊爺唔願意繼續留喺遭受戰火蹂躪8年嘅中國 就斷然嚟咗香港 之後生咗爸<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">195?</span><br />\n爸好細個幾歲嘅時候 做走私客嘅爺爺畀船槳打死咗 (有冇歴史學家可以答我有咩好走私 唔好答我奶粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 所以啊嫲就咁掉低咗佢 佢唯有同叔叔相依為命 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">時間去到60年代</span><br />\n叔叔喺舊屏山警處做㕑師 而叔&amp;爸就寄住喺警處入面 仲話返學有得搭警處順風車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爸讀過屏山公立達德學校 讀到小四 a pen a man就冇讀 要去打吓工求生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2nM226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2nM226.jpg&h=838186b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係爸記憶中嘅警車 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvgRuKo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvgRuKo.png&h=2f32c2dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屏山警處 當時元朗仲係一個小市鎮 警處起喺屏山圍村人上面 好明顯係要㩒住啲有權有勢有槍有炮有地有樓嘅牛屎佬 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">唔知咩年代</span><br />\n之後就住喺元朗塘坊邨一帶 佢由基本地盤工做到管工 佢話佢有份起元朗警處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">後記</span><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">好多香港人喺做香港人之前都係睇唔到前路</span> 好多都係走難落嚟 <br />\n<br />\n估唔到100年之後 又要走多次 <br />\n想藉呢次機會同大家講 <span class=\"blue\">唔好以為走嗰時要拋棄嘅嘢留喺到就唔會消失</span><br />\n<br />\n你哋心中不捨嘅香港或許早已不復存在<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真正嘅香港精神係 在看不見的道路上仍然敢於奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n無論係走唔走嘅人都好 祝你幸福<br />\n希望你真正咁活出香港人嘅精神 而唔係賭氣要格硬留喺到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yM2BEJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yM2BEJ.png&h=37274180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Q9C9ZK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Q9C9ZK.jpg&h=eb33d142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWEzsMq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWEzsMq.jpg&h=02499d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XpevLx6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXpevLx6.jpg&h=d1214246&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f7540c40f2e62a92fc9819c5573b6d4c1e574ca","tid":2121785,"uid":309331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"sauce <br />\n<br />\n舊時香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/oldhkstory/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Foldhkstory%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCAx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=0af09d7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/oldhkstory/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人的香港史 蔡榮芳<br />\n<br />\nHISTORY &ndash; A Brief Visual History of HK Police Vehicles &amp; Uniforms<br />\n<a href=\"http://hongwrong.com/police-uniforms-vehicles/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhongwrong.com%2Fpolice-uniforms-vehicles%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCAx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=163174b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hongwrong.com/police-uniforms-vehicles/</a>"},{"pid":"617ef1b93421e77dd24375fa3c4387fe594b9c4c","tid":2121785,"uid":76710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"無靈魂、得番個殼嘅香港，仲叫唔叫我地所認識嘅香港？"},{"pid":"067d31e08c1c68929652a43a5db21a63e039c458","tid":2121785,"uid":309331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:16:37.000Z","msg":"頭半段講香港史係想講話香港人本身就係走難落嚟 而家唔好因為一時意氣而唔走因小失大 1999先道個歉<br />\n<br />\n利申 我唔走嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0453075200d8df735159f377f96e4391350b3334","tid":2121785,"uid":309331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"617ef1b93421e77dd24375fa3c4387fe594b9c4c","tid":2121785,"uid":76710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"無靈魂、得番個殼嘅香港，仲叫唔叫我地所認識嘅香港？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"好多人因為香港情懷而想守住呢個家園 奈何香港本身已經變咗好多<br />\n<br />\n養活我哋嘅事物 都蠶食咗我哋嘅靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985cd279bec7ea7db1c0dec578c177ded4094da1","tid":2121785,"uid":309331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"打到1999冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"067d31e08c1c68929652a43a5db21a63e039c458","tid":2121785,"uid":309331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:16:37.000Z","msg":"頭半段講香港史係想講話香港人本身就係走難落嚟 而家唔好因為一時意氣而唔走因小失大 1999先道個歉<br />\n<br />\n利申 我唔走嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}